==English==
===Etymology===
*From Old English [[toye]].

===Pronunciation===
*{{audio|en-us-toy.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Noun===
'''toy''' (''plural:'' [[toys]])

#something to [[play]] with, esp. as intended for use by a [[child]].
#a thing of little [[importance]] or [[value]]: [[trifle]].

